com.zendesk.sdk.model.helpcenter

Class Section

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zendesk.sdk.model.helpcenter.Section
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Section
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This is a model class for a Section object that will be created by the HelpCenterProvider.

    This class is a model that will be serialised to JSON and deserialised from JSON to this model. As such it does not follow the m naming prefix for fields.
